--==Ecrase==--
Copyright (c) 2014 jmf

Ecrase is the "Ecrase Creative R* Adventure Scripting Engine".
It is written in C++ with SDL2 for graphics and will allow scripting own point-and-click adventure games.
Ecrase is released under the MIT license.


The meaning of the "R" in ecrase is a secret. ;)

Compiling:
mkdir bin
cd bin
cmake ..
make

Run with ./ecrase while in the bin/ directory.


